nodes.text: A female Medoslean patient was being cared for at the Starlight Beacon's medcenter in the aftermath of the Great Hyperspace Disaster. While being treated by Doctor Gino'le and junior nurse Okana, the patient had a violent negative response to something she was administered. The ensuing commotion was used by Ambassador Ceeril, another patient in the medcenter, to stage an assassination attempt against himself which he intended to pin on the facility's two Hassarian patients.
